        {
          "id": "acd90b9e-8e0c-4ace-ae73-da98cd4e61fa",
          "question": "What does Evergreen Systems actually handle?",
          "answer": "Evergreen Systems builds, runs, and manages the entire outbound system end-to-end.\nThis includes targeting, outreach, follow-ups, automation, and ongoing optimization.\nYour only responsibility is showing up to qualified sales calls booked directly into your calendar.",
          "position": 0,
          "created_at": "2025-12-16T17:14:50.3744+00:00",
          "updated_at": "2025-12-16T17:14:50.3744+00:00",
          "_junction": {
            "id": "505ab616-7b92-4d06-b95c-19a9caa9fa3d",
            "section_id": "0769ace9-62dc-47cd-9231-5295178623c4",
            "faq_item_id": "acd90b9e-8e0c-4ace-ae73-da98cd4e61fa",
            "position": 0,
            "created_at": "2025-12-16T17:14:58.698262+00:00",
            "status": "published"
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "7211c98d-e4ab-4346-b014-63106849b8c6",
          "question": "How does your performance guarantee work?",
          "answer": "Our engagements are performance-aligned.\nOnce the system is fully live, you’re only charged for months where we deliver the agreed minimum number of qualified, attended calls.\nIf that minimum isn’t met in a given month, you’re not charged for that period.",
          "position": 0,
          "created_at": "2025-12-16T17:15:37.824277+00:00",
          "updated_at": "2025-12-16T17:15:37.824277+00:00",
          "_junction": {
            "id": "fe79799f-1d2b-41fa-923a-603bb76aa2c8",
            "section_id": "0769ace9-62dc-47cd-9231-5295178623c4",
            "faq_item_id": "7211c98d-e4ab-4346-b014-63106849b8c6",
            "position": 1,
            "created_at": "2025-12-16T17:15:57.636139+00:00",
            "status": "published"
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "f39cf81a-7e14-41c5-aaaa-6985f31530c9",
          "question": "How quickly does the system start delivering calls?",
          "answer": "Every engagement begins with a short setup phase where we build, configure, and safely prepare your outbound infrastructure.\nThis typically takes 2–3 weeks, after which the system goes live and starts generating initial replies and conversations.",
          "position": 6,
          "created_at": "2025-12-16T17:16:04.335948+00:00",
          "updated_at": "2025-12-18T01:43:56.394606+00:00",
          "_junction": {
            "id": "05980fca-3606-426a-be47-66dd81d91fad",
            "section_id": "0769ace9-62dc-47cd-9231-5295178623c4",
            "faq_item_id": "f39cf81a-7e14-41c5-aaaa-6985f31530c9",
            "position": 2,
            "created_at": "2025-12-16T17:16:04.525086+00:00",
            "status": "published"
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "2ccba07f-18ed-48a6-a92b-84ce84fd1e0b",
          "question": "How involved do I need to be?",
          "answer": "Very little.\nWe handle setup, execution, and ongoing optimization end-to-end.\nYour only responsibility is showing up to qualified sales calls once the system is live.",
          "position": 7,
          "created_at": "2025-12-16T17:16:28.942785+00:00",
          "updated_at": "2025-12-18T01:45:54.198006+00:00",
          "_junction": {
            "id": "de4b4ca6-3efa-4292-a389-f477789aad13",
            "section_id": "0769ace9-62dc-47cd-9231-5295178623c4",
            "faq_item_id": "2ccba07f-18ed-48a6-a92b-84ce84fd1e0b",
            "position": 3,
            "created_at": "2025-12-16T17:16:29.093495+00:00",
            "status": "published"
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "5d5b67bc-3c0f-465b-a82a-f451d7f54aad",
          "question": "Is this a one-time campaign or an ongoing system?",
          "answer": "This is an ongoing outbound system, not a one-off campaign.\nPerformance improves over time as data compounds and targeting is refined.\nMost clients stay engaged for multiple months to build a consistent, predictable acquisition channel.",
          "position": 8,
          "created_at": "2025-12-16T17:18:11.818+00:00",
          "updated_at": "2025-12-16T17:18:24.371502+00:00",
          "_junction": {
            "id": "b239d37e-9109-4f30-8206-54c07c1de8a4",
            "section_id": "0769ace9-62dc-47cd-9231-5295178623c4",
            "faq_item_id": "5d5b67bc-3c0f-465b-a82a-f451d7f54aad",
            "position": 4,
            "created_at": "2025-12-16T17:18:11.979662+00:00",
            "status": "published"
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "7d78310e-cac8-49c1-a15a-387094a3b076",
          "question": "Who is this a good fit for — and who isn’t?",
          "answer": "This works best for B2B companies with a clear offer and the capacity to handle new sales conversations.\nIt’s not a fit for businesses without follow-up capability or those looking for instant, short-term spikes.",
          "position": 9,
          "created_at": "2025-12-16T17:18:29.922556+00:00",
          "updated_at": "2025-12-16T17:18:45.478458+00:00",
